						Fwife : Frugalware Installer Frontend Readme

Fwife 0.1 beta

Warning : Beta version - Caution - Many bugs, segfaults and memory leaks are possible. Use for testing only.

This version only support netinstall because it's necessary for fwlive. I will see after for a local version.

Knows Bugs : 

Select plugin : -> graphical bug with packet description label when description too long.

General : -> Some stock icons are not loaded in configuration part when gtk is not installed on target (due to chroot()).

TODO :

