General : -> Verify C code, remove useless parts, simplify code if possible !

Ideas :

-> Made new configuration plugin for selecting default desktop manager (xdm, gdm, kdm) and default window manager
-> Improve gui (dialogbox for exemple)
-> Improve help (add tooltip text, etc...)

Text (dialogbox, labels, help widget) need to be write/rewrite with a good english :p

Compiling and testing : Just do a 'make' in source directory then do './fwife' :p

Any suggestions or patchs are welcome ;)

